Final Assessment: Maha Vikas Aghadi Predicted to Win Maharashtra Elections 2024

The Maharashtra Elections 2024 are poised to be a closely contested race between two powerful alliances: Maha Vikas Aghadi (MVA) and Maha Yuti (MY). Based on astrological analysis, it is anticipated that Maha Vikas Aghadi will secure 149 seats, while Maha Yuti is expected to garner 139 seats. With 145 seats required to form a government in the 288-seat Maharashtra Legislature, Maha Vikas Aghadi appears to have the edge in this election.

Final Assessment: Maha Vikas Aghadi Predicted to Win Maharashtra Elections 2024

The Maharashtra Elections 2024 are poised to be a closely contested race between two powerful alliances: Maha Vikas Aghadi (MVA) and Maha Yuti (MY). Based on astrological analysis, it is anticipated that Maha Vikas Aghadi will secure 149 seats, while Maha Yuti is expected to garner 139 seats. With 145 seats required to form a government in the 288-seat Maharashtra Legislature, Maha Vikas Aghadi appears to have the edge in this election.
